= SDL_HINT_VIDEO_X11_XVIDMODE =
A hint that specifies whether the X11 !VidMode extension should be used.




== Values ==
{|
|0
|disable XVidMode
|-
|1
|enable XVidMode
|}


== Default ==
By default SDL will use XVidMode if it is available.



